@startuml svc-safety-compliance--post-waivers

!include ../theme.puml
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #dc2626
}

header [[/microservices/svc-safety-compliance/#integration-context ⬆ svc-safety-compliance Integration Context]]

title POST /waivers\nGuest signs safety waiver\n<size:10><color:#7c3aed>ARCHITECT OVERRIDE — enriched with identity verification and signature gate</color></size>

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-safety-compliance" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-safety-compliance/]] #FEE2E2
participant "Guest Profiles" as GP [[/microservices/svc-guest-profiles/]] #EDE9FE
participant "DocuSign" as DS #F3E8FF
participant "Notifications" as Ntfy [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #F1F5F9
database "PostgreSQL" as DB [[/microservices/svc-safety-compliance/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-safety-compliance.html View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /waivers
activate GW #dc2626
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #dc2626

note right of Svc : Validate waiver request\n(guest_id, waiver_type,\nadventure_category required)

== Duplicate Waiver Check ==

Svc -> DB : SELECT FROM waivers\nWHERE guest_id = ?\nAND waiver_type = ?\nAND status = ACTIVE\nAND expires_at > NOW()
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Existing waivers (if any)
deactivate DB

alt Active waiver already exists
    note right of Svc #FEF3C7 : Return 409 Conflict\nGuest already has valid\nwaiver of this type
    Svc --> GW : 409 Conflict\n(existing_waiver_id, expires_at)
    deactivate Svc
    GW --> Client : 409 Conflict
    deactivate GW
else No active waiver — proceed

    == Identity Verification ==

    Svc -> GP : [[/microservices/svc-guest-profiles/#get-guestsguest_id-get-guest-profile GET /guests/{guest_id}]]
    activate GP #EDE9FE
    GP --> Svc : Guest profile\n(name, DOB, ID document status)
    deactivate GP

    note right of Svc : Verify guest is 18+\nor has guardian consent\nVerify ID document is validated

    alt Guest under 18, no guardian consent
        note right of Svc #FEE2E2 : Reject: minor without\nguardian consent on file
        Svc --> GW : 422 Unprocessable\n(reason: GUARDIAN_CONSENT_REQUIRED)
        deactivate Svc
        GW --> Client : 422 Unprocessable
        deactivate GW
    end

    == Digital Signature (DocuSign) ==

    Svc -> DS : Verify digital signature\n(signature_payload, document_hash,\nguest identity)
    activate DS #F3E8FF
    alt Signature valid
        DS --> Svc : Signature verified\n(envelope_id, signed_at)
        deactivate DS
    else Signature invalid or expired
        DS --> Svc : Verification failed\n(reason)
        deactivate DS
        note right of Svc #FEE2E2 : Reject: invalid signature\nGuest must re-sign
        Svc --> GW : 422 Unprocessable\n(reason: SIGNATURE_INVALID)
        deactivate Svc
        GW --> Client : 422 Unprocessable
        deactivate GW
    end

    == Database ==

    Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO waivers\n(waiver_id, guest_id, waiver_type,\nadventure_category, envelope_id,\nsigned_at, expires_at,\nstatus = ACTIVE)
    activate DB #FEF9C3
    DB --> Svc : Created row
    deactivate DB

    == Async Confirmation ==

    Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Send waiver copy to guest email]]

    Svc --> GW : 201 Created\n(waiver_id, status = ACTIVE,\nexpires_at)
    deactivate Svc
    GW --> Client : 201 Created
    deactivate GW
end

@enduml
